snippet.title: Diana and Roma Pretend Play Police
snippet.description:
Diana pretend play as a cop and pretends to put Roma in her jail playhouse tent toy. Roma threw trash outside in a no littering zone, so he had to go to jail. After that, Roma was picking flowers at a garden that didn’t allow people to remove flowers and was fishing in a no fishing zone and had to go to the jail playhouse for a few minutes. In the end, Diana was tired of being a cop, more fun being a kid!
